    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Having a good, solid rope could come in handy in just about any outdoor emergency situation, so why not keep some around your waist? Be prepared for any adventure turned emergency with this every day survival gear ParaLace 550 Survival Paracord Duty Belt. Ideal for both essential preparedness and tactical applications, you never know when you&#039;ll have to improvise in the field. With over 100 feet of unraveled paracord you can rig a tent, make a fire-starter bow, set snares, go fishing, repair gear, and much more. There are many creative places to store paracord but wearing it around your waist is one of the the most practical</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Survival EDC 550 Paracord Belt with Stainless Steel Buckle</h2>\n  <p>Having a good, solid rope could come in handy in just about any outdoor emergency situation, so why not keep some around your waist?</p>\n  <p>Be prepared for any adventure turned emergency with this every day survival gear ParaLace 550 Survival Paracord Duty Belt. Ideal for both essential preparedness and tactical applications, you never know when you&#039;ll have to improvise in the field. With over 100 feet of unraveled paracord you can rig a tent, make a fire-starter bow, set snares, go fishing, repair gear, and much more. There are many creative places to store paracord but wearing it around your waist is one of the the most practical. Use the unraveled paracord to tie a load to the roof of your car, hang your gear from a tree while camping or even make a sling in a pinch to get off a mountain in a real emergency.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>UNIVERSAL FIT MENS BELT:</strong> One size fits all; 52 inches in total length; extra length can be tucked within belt loops or cut to fit while singeing the ends; very adjustable and comfortable; no pre-made belt holes, just stick the belt clasp through the paracord weave wherever it fits most comfortably for best fit</li>\n    <li><strong>PARACORD BELT SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Unraveled Total Length: 110 feet; Belt Waist Length: 52 inches; Belt Width: 1.5 inches; Stainless Steel Belt Buckle; Color: Black Paracord Belt</li>\n    <li><strong>THE ULTIMATE EDC SURVIVAL BELT:</strong> Unravel the paracord braided weave to provide a rope source of strong survival cord at your disposal to craft a weapon, build a stretcher, fish for food, build a shelter and much more</li>\n    <li><strong>FASHIONABLE DESIGN:</strong> While being highly dependable and extremely versatile this piece of survival gear can be worn everyday for when the most unexpected situations may arise</li>\n    <li><strong>EASY TO MAINTAIN:</strong> Fully washable, easy to clean; wash, rinse and repeat; can be run through the washing machine and air dried</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72059/GH8HVWwQnJEsnBHWeDyteLI26ZFqIH-metaNzFiMTV2RFNnVkwuanBn-.jpg\" alt=\"Having a good, solid rope could come in handy in just about any outdoor emergency situation, so why not keep some around your waist\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> PLCPCB</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058488022</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 52 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>These survival gear paracord belts are constructed of highly durable Milspec 550 Tactical Paracord; is made from 7 Stands of 100% genuine Mil-Spec 550lb parachute cord. The same stuff used by the US Military. It has a breaking strength of 550lbs with a working load of 220lbs. The overall thickness of the parachute cord line is 5/32&quot; diameter and has a consistent stretch of just 10% elongation under loaded weight in product tests.</p>\n  <p>Each wilderness survival belt features a stainless steel belt buckle, that locks in your desired waist length at any interval you desire. These paracord belts are a universal fit as they are very adjustable; no pre-made belt holes, just stick the belt clasp through the paracord weave wherever it fits most comfortably for best fit.</p>\n  <p>Beef up your bug out bag with this essential piece of daily gear, the ParaLace paracord belt.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Having a good, solid rope could come in handy in just about any outdoor emergency situation, so why not keep some around your waist? Be prepared for any adventure turned emergency with this every day survival gear ParaLace 550 Survival Paracord Duty Belt. Ideal for both essential preparedness and tactical applications, you never know when you'll have to improvise in the field. With over 100 feet of unraveled paracord you can rig a tent, make a fire-starter bow, set snares, go fishing, repair gear, and much more. There are many creative places to store paracord but wearing it around your waist is one of the the most practical.",
